P9W5Zhe5Nz8.description:
In this message, Rev'd Peter Alabi explains how doubt, unbelief, anxiety, fear, bitterness, fear, forgetfulness, and disorderliness are ways by which men assist the devil on earth. The truth is that the devil has no power over believers, but he can use all of these to get through. We have the absolute power to resist the devil in prayer. 

Be edified as Rev'd Peter Alabi teaches on the topic 'Resisting the Devil in Prayer' which is the fourth part in the January series - Everything by Prayer.
